{"tid":1192411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要事項】聽日見到人搞事一定要影底佢！","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T11:58:54.000Z","uid":88840,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13d6f1dd56ddf3b9e2f0351f06f37036843d219c","tid":1192411,"uid":88840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"香港勝在自私嘅人同傻閪太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到呢個時候仲諗緊著咩色衫，唔好做激進嘢比位人入，唔該用下你哋個豬閪腦，有心做你，是但搵個二打六係你隔離衝擊再賴話係你帶頭都得啦！<br />\n<br />\n我明個個都唔願做犧牲嗰個，但出得嚟連比人拉嘅覺悟都冇，咁驚青不如唔好出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，遊行只係所有革命嘅第一步，當所有人都自私想保身，永遠都唔會有下一步，所以聽日如果你哋見到有人搞事，拎個相機出嚟影底，不過係影底你自己，問下你自己條柒頭，為咗香港你可以犧牲幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預期諗做乜會比人拉，不如諗下比人拉之後嘅應對。要贏就要有人用血肉換，你唔做犧牲嗰個ok，但最起碼唔好拖後腿落井下石，聽日見各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f47a2601c227a9967b0a25e8e23498dae03de77","tid":1192411,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\n不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}